      "personalSkillId": "draconic_heir",
      "notes": [
        {
          "text": "Kana's gender is always opposite Corrin's. The selected spouse resolves Kana's growths, caps, traits, class inheritance, sibling, and support bonuses.",
          "textZhHans": "神流的性别始终与神威相反。所选配偶决定神流的成长率、上限、属性、职业继承、兄弟姐妹与支援加成。"
        },
        {
          "text": "If Corrin marries an offspring unit, that spouse's own variable parent must also be selected before Kana's inherited data is fully resolved.",
          "textZhHans": "若神威与子女单位结婚，则需先选定该配偶自身的可变父母，神流的继承数据才能完全解析。"
        },
        {
          "text": "Male Corrin with Niles or female Corrin with Rhajat does not unlock Dragon Blood and produces no Kana.",
          "textZhHans": "男神威与零，或女神威与莎拉的组合不会解锁「龙之血」，也不会诞生神流。"
        }
      ]
    },
